            </li>

            <li>
              <p>
                Apply the definition:
                <md>
                  <mrow>\proj wx \amp = \frac{\dotp wx}{\dotp xx}\vec x</mrow>
                  <mrow>\amp = \frac{6}{3}\la 1,1,1\ra</mrow>
